Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:03.70,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,3600)\bord2.25\3c&H1F1F1F&\be6\c&HFFFFFC&}so ra no wo to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.85,0:00:13.52,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}The brilliant glow of this sky, does it carry right into your heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.83,0:00:22.91,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,1600)\3c&H141414&}The melody you heard in your dream, it plays like the silence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:28.12,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Even if your hands are still far from that dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.12,0:00:33.34,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Come now and remember that kindly voice
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.34,0:00:46.28,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(50,200)\3c&H141414&}Someone was there singing for you, the happiness they sang about
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.28,0:00:55.68,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Sound of the sky, echo on high, break through that overwhelming sadness
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.68,0:01:00.62,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)\3c&H141414&}Everything that shines in your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.62,0:01:06.08,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,400)\3c&H141414&}Is part of the real world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.34,0:01:15.55,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(100,200)\3c&H141414&}Even your tears can't leave you here to stay forever
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.71,0:01:27.51,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,4000)\3c&H141414&}In this gentle light pouring down onto you, play tomorrow's song
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.18,0:02:50.19,Sora OP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&HFFFFFF&\1a&00&}A Day in the Life - Rio Runs
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.46,0:22:46.53,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - put these feelings together
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.53,0:22:49.32,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)}And sing of how important they are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.67,0:23:07.80,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I was so happy that I cried
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.64,0:23:13.77,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It hurt so bad that I laughed
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.60,0:23:22.61,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}But that all just goes to show that I'm alive
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.61,0:23:26.74,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,800)}Let's just walk it slowly
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.74,0:23:28.43,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}Everybody singing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.43,0:23:32.72,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Just tell me a bit of what you think
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:34.04,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&}You're just my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:40.05,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Love and friendship - even though they might waver
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.08,0:23:40.05,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}I know, you know, little happy
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.05,0:23:45.88,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I want us to echo on forever
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.79,0:23:45.88,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\3c&HE5A9EA&\an8}Can you hear my precious note?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.88,0:23:52.26,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}All these words that there are can't even describe it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.26,0:23:58.01,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.01,0:24:02.65,Sora ED,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,1400)}Can you hear it? Our harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.89,0:02:45.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like something that might wake the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:54.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.24,0:03:01.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.32,0:03:06.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It tastes great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.96,0:03:09.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It's delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:12.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,At least it's edible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.59,0:03:14.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:17.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a traditional food in my village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.37,0:03:22.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is that miso thing? And it's made the same way as soy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.12,0:03:22.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.96,0:03:25.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought some miso that my mother made.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:30.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There's still a lot more, so eat as much as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.34,0:03:36.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To Treize?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.83,0:03:37.82,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:41.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We finally received word from the Supply Corps.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.70,0:03:45.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha and I will go to pick them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:51.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to run out of ammunition, medical supplies, and daily necessities.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.42,0:03:54.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now we can rest easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.28,0:03:55.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Noël?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Carl's workshop, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.81,0:04:00.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.34,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.11,0:04:05.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're getting a full workout on that bugle this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.49,0:04:08.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.83,0:04:44.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heref youf hoof.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.85,0:04:46.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:51.26,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are your manners?\NWouldn't your dad cry if he saw you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh... Wike a' cabe
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.92,0:05:07.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, for your tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:11.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortune cookies?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:14.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You really can't stand them, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.05,0:05:17.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But you can't blame those kids at the church.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:24.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone who takes advantage of worthless superstitions to get some sort of profit is the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.22,0:05:27.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:29.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones here taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:34.64,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.17,0:05:46.65,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But Kanata has really gotten used to this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.65,0:05:49.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's always trying so hard. It's cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:51.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.31,0:05:54.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to admit she's diligent and full of enthusiasm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.41,0:05:59.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not the type to think you can get by with just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:04.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you giving me that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.92,0:06:06.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.89,0:06:12.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Quit playing me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.71,0:06:23.77,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.69,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It might take a while to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.69,0:06:29.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got you. Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.25,0:06:33.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any problems for Rio, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.40,0:06:34.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.29,0:06:36.13,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Commencing operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.06,0:06:42.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Drive carefully!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.25,0:06:57.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't expect you to be able to do this, but controlling the note with just the mouthpiece is one of the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.51,0:06:59.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:05.45,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.19,0:07:13.16,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How's life in the fort so far?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:18.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lax enough to say it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.01,0:07:21.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost kind of jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.85,0:07:28.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,While we're still on it, why'd you enlist in the army?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.97,0:07:32.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.28,0:07:36.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard I could learn how to play an instrument for free.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.38,0:07:42.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but I also thought that it was important to protect my country!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:46.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind. Even if it's for money or whatever,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.98,0:07:52.89,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,the ones with some ambition stay around longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:56.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... I'm honored...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.04,0:08:02.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why did you join?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.46,0:08:09.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Me? Well, probably the opposite of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.99,0:08:13.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They are pretty hard to find these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:18.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't hear brass instruments much outside the army.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.81,0:08:21.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard one a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.38,0:08:25.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just... like... yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:26.02,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.02,0:08:30.05,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound... of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.42,0:08:40.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.60,0:08:41.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Pull yourself together, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.00,0:08:45.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.99,0:09:01.23,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, just stay still.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.72,0:09:05.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot, Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.98,0:09:07.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, you'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.29,0:09:19.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mo-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.45,0:09:26.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kanata?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:29.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:34.76,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to eat... snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.93,0:09:38.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Wait right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.48,0:09:49.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Snow. Snow. Snow. Where's the snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.44,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why the hell would we have snow?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.13,0:09:56.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:09:59.87,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:10.86,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No. That's the last resort.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.75,0:10:18.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine. Medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:22.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Medicine!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:24.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.81,0:10:28.41,SoraAlt,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just about to run out...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.11,0:10:31.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Those idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn the Supply Corps!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:38.40,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I can't do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.32,0:10:42.00,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:20.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an3\pos(1840,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.95,0:11:25.95,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H000000&\bord0\an1\pos(80,1050)}Sound of the Sky
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.51,0:11:59.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:02.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope the children didn't cause you any-
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:06.70,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for my past disrespect!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.70,0:12:08.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.65,0:12:11.29,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.48,0:12:24.68,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Drink this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.75,0:12:27.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:38.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Her fever is a bit high, but it should fall now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.27,0:12:41.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a serious disease at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:44.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's roseola.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Roseola? Only kids catch that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:52.97,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Adults can catch it under extreme fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.05,0:12:58.50,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When we take in new children,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.50,0:13:00.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,a lot of them catch it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.65,0:13:05.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The healthier they look, the higher the fever goes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.55,0:13:09.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably been hiding it the whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.67,0:13:13.59,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Then... will Kanata get better?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:15.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,She won't stay like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:17.81,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I think she'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.78,0:13:23.57,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.02,0:13:29.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.96,0:13:31.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:35.08,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Yumina.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.72,0:13:37.42,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:42.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is made with medicinal herbs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.58,0:13:46.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Please have her drink some later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:53.32,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Thank you for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.41,0:13:55.94,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.94,0:14:01.75,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,To serve the people of this town is our joy and our duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.92,0:14:06.91,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,May the blessings of all be upon you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you for your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.08,0:16:13.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.43,0:16:18.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:21.46,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:32.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just like miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.73,0:16:34.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The soup?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.07,0:16:35.63,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.63,0:16:37.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,miso dregs are...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.55,0:16:41.01,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,When you make the soup, you strain the miso.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.01,0:16:43.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The beans and things that are left - dregs.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:48.98,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A leftover, or extra baggage. Like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:55.83,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been like that since I was a kid. That's why... I decided to try harder.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.83,0:16:59.24,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I wouldn't make problems for everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.91,0:17:01.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.49,0:17:08.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a lot more complex than you look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:11.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And selfish and spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:18.43,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I... say things?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.56,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.07,0:17:32.15,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right, Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.15,0:17:34.21,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.21,0:17:37.20,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That piece you were just humming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:39.67,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:41.58,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,It went like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.33,0:17:58.25,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm speechless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.25,0:18:00.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,After hearing it just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.28,0:18:02.71,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.71,0:18:06.31,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A long time ago, I heard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.31,0:18:10.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to play that piece myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.19,0:18:13.18,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I want to...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:18.49,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A sound that seems to echo from the heavens. That piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.03,0:18:23.19,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But miso dregs
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.19,0:18:25.79,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,are miso dregs no matter what you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.79,0:18:27.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:32.80,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't just leave ourselves indebted to some church.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.53,0:18:36.96,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This Takemicaduchi is a treasure from another era.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.96,0:18:41.07,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,There are thousands of secrets just sleeping inside it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.07,0:18:42.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Secrets?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.38,0:18:46.06,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Right. If you want to know more, ask Noël later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.85,0:19:01.53,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This should be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.53,0:19:03.03,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.68,0:19:17.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.93,0:19:58.99,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably what the whole piece really sounds like.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.99,0:20:03.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,All sorts of instruments, different parts ringing together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.36,0:20:05.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,They become a single music.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.16,0:20:08.22,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like riding a tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:12.47,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,A commander, a gunner, a driver,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.47,0:20:14.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and communications personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.38,0:20:18.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone works together to work a single tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.11,0:20:20.85,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,No one is unneeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.85,0:20:24.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a single note is unneeded.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:33.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look at me like that. Someone said it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:36.36,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The person I look up to,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.36,0:20:38.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and honor most.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:41.28,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,As she told me,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.28,0:20:42.73,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.73,0:20:46.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think seniority and superiors exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:50.35,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So that those in lower ranks can make problems for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.60,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to be able right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.65,0:20:57.39,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,0)}But just remember your frustration and powerlessness,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.39,0:21:01.11,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,and the happiness of having someone to care for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.11,0:21:05.62,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, when you have to take care of someone, that will be
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:07.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,your experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.17,0:21:12.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,So make as many problems for me as you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.55,0:21:14.37,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I made the same ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.32,0:21:19.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, when you do something wrong, you'll be scolded and punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.33,0:21:23.38,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you're suffering, if your heart might break, tell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:26.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.64,0:21:33.55,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:37.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on, I will make as many problems for you as I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.27,0:21:39.48,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to go easy on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.12,0:21:54.12,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on. I should have stayed here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.12,0:21:58.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kanata, getting Rio to nurse her back to health...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:02.14,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it wasn't a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.14,0:22:05.88,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And it looks like it's just fatigue. She'll be fine if she sleeps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.28,0:22:14.41,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,The Takemicaduchi's lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.41,0:22:18.10,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I used it for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.10,0:22:20.09,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I do it at a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:23.92,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,You listened to that piece, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.01,0:22:25.78,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.76,0:22:29.51,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,And you said you wouldn't listen to it ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.51,0:22:32.27,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to hear it just once.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.83,0:22:36.04,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.58,0:22:39.33,SoraDefault,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a secret.
